$interpreted: Turtle Chieftain: What are those people saying?
Respectful Turtle-Tribe Soldier: They're gossiping about the Edensnatch, sir.
Respectful Turtle-Tribe Soldier: People are saying that the Alliance must be covering up for the Capybara Tribe, else they'd have issued a refutation over something as big as this.
Turtle Chieftain: ...Those idiots are playing with fire, and now it's us who are up to our necks in it.
Turtle Chieftain: ...That won't do. Go, to the Alliance!
???: Hello.
Secret Society Boss: I'm on the way to the Alliance myself, shall we go together? I have some business to discuss with you, as it happens.
Yan-Bo: (It's been a few days already, and I've still not heard anything about the investigations from the Chieftain yet...)
Yan-Bo: (I should go and check out the situation myself...)
Surprised Beast: Hey, there's a new development to the Edensnatch story!
Doubtful Beast: What, you mean the Capybara Tribe really did cheat?
Surprised Beast: Yup, the Alliance just announced that the Capybaras fixed the competition, that Yan-Bo broke the rules and committed murder, and that the whole thing was a sham!
Yan-Bo: (What... a sham!? Broke the rules and committed murder!?)
Surprised Beast: I also saw a group of Secret Society hoodlums on their way to the Capybaras. They looked fierce and were carrying weapons. I'm afraid something's going down!
Yan-Bo: (Oh no, I better get back to the Tribe and see what's happened!)
Nervous Capybara: What are you doing here?!
Sennosuke: Round 'em all up!
Sennosuke: Is this everybody from the village? Where's Yan-Bo!?
Boss's Henchman: That's everyone. He's not here.
Sennosuke: Did he hear we were coming and flee? You lot, conduct a search!
Vigilant Hoodlum: This guy was trying to sneak away, he must know something!
Edensnatch Manager: ...What are you gonna do with me!?
Sennosuke: You're...
Edensnatch Manager: You're that guy from the Edensnatch...! I told you, Kaito's death was an accident, why have you come here!?
Sennosuke: An accident? Before he died, Master said,
Sennosuke: that dirtbag Yan-Bo tricked him and made him fall!
Edensnatch Manager: W-well you should be looking for Yan-Bo then, not coming here! G-go find Yan-Bo if it's revenge you're after...
Sennosuke: So I've come to ask you where he's gone to!
Edensnatch Manager: M-me? I dunno where he's run to...
Sennosuke: Oh, so you're not willing to talk, are you?
Edensnatch Manager: I don't know... I really don't know!!
Sennosuke: Do you think I'm a fool? You two are in on this together!
Edensnatch Manager: I confess, I confess! We wanted to ensure Yan-Bo's victory so that we could sell even more of our Capybara Tinctures...
Sennosuke: Tinctures?
Edensnatch Manager: W-we lost so many Edensnatches that nobody wanted to buy our medicines anymore...
Edensnatch Manager: If Yan-Bo won, then the other Tribes would surely look up to us again... Look! See how poor our village is...
Sennosuke: Poor?!
Sennosuke: This is all because you're poor? Master and I were poor, too! What the hell do you liars take us for?
Sennosuke: My Master's died...
Sennosuke: All for your deceit and greed!
Sennosuke: Kill every Capybara here, and then send somebody to keep watch. That Yan-Bo can't stay away forever!
Panicked Capybara: S-stay away from me!
Panicked Capybara: Aahhhh!!!!
